reviewText: My kids love this video and I love it because it's clean, family friendly and not scary to anyone. The kids go around singing the songs from the video all day long.

My son Malachi absolute loves this movie! They are all awesome videos, He loves all the music and looking for Bullfrog in Find Bullfrog. We watch this video or any of the the 4 in the series 2 or 3 times a day! A great variety of Christian hit songs and up beat videos! Awesome! If you like Baby Einstein  or Praise Baby videos you will love these too!
